Include finemapr R package & others

load_all("~/git/variani/finemapr")
options(finemapr_finemap = "~/apps/finemap/finemap")

library(gaston)

Fine-mapping example with 2 causal SNPs

We replictaed the example provided with the FINEMAP software. See http://www.christianbenner.com/.

ex <- example_finemap()

out <- run_finemap(ex$tab1, ex$ld1, ex$n1)
plot(out, label_size = 3, grid_ncol = 1)
